data.description: Ready to move in farmhouse style home situated on over 2 acres in a great location! Too many updates to list; newer flooring, cabinets, paint, windows, bathtubs, toilets, furnace, new hot water heater, newer washer, dryer, & stove. All appliances stay! Only a few minutes to Waverly. 2 bedroom 2 full bath. 12x34 outdoor building.  Back yard has fenced area for pets/animals. Beautiful country setting with the convenience of nearby town!
